Package com.example.vortex_app.model

Class Event

java.lang.Object
com.example.vortex_app.model.Event
All Implemented Interfaces:
Serializable
public class Event extends Object implements Serializable
Represents an event with various details such as name, location, time, price, and more. This class is used to map data from Firestore to an Event object for further manipulation.
